---
import '../styles/bootstrap.scss';
import ToTopButton from '../components/ToTopButton.astro';
interface Props {
  title: string;
}

const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="description" content="Astro description" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.png" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>{title} - 華夏資源開發股分有限公司</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <section class="container-fluid">
        <div class="header__content-wrap">
          <div class="header__logo">
            <img src="/nav-hsrd-logo.png" alt="華夏資源Logo" />
          </div>
          <ul class="header__menu">
            <li>
              <a class="header__menu-link" href="/">關於我們</a>
            </li>
            <!-- <li>
              <a class="header__menu-link" href="/about">公司介紹</a>
            </li> -->
            <li>
              <a class="header__menu-link" href="/service-list">服務內容</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a class="header__menu-link" href="/gallery-list">案件與工程實績</a>
            </li>
            <!-- <li>
              <a class="header__menu-link" href="/news-list">最新消息</a>
            </li> -->
            <li>
              <a class="header__menu-link" href="/contact">聯絡我們</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </header>
    <main class="main">
      <div class="container">
        <slot />
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="footer">
      <section class="container-fluid">
        <div class="footer__logo">
          <img class="footer__logo-image" src="/footer-water-logo.png" alt="華夏Logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="footer__description">
          <p>
            華夏資源開發的核心技術團隊，專注於海水淡化設備開發設計，擁有自主研發能力與豐富的海水淡化廠操作維運經驗。
          </p>
          <p>同時，本公司也提供各產業水處理與資源化再利用之評估與技術諮詢。</p>
          <p>
            在客製化的解決方案中，我們會根據客戶的主觀需求與客觀環境，將水資源價值最大化，注重每個工序細節，實現減廢零排目標。
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-0">© 華夏資源開發股份有限公司</p>
      </section>
    </footer>
    <!-- <ToTopButton style="background-color: pink;" /> -->
    <ToTopButton />
  </body>
</html>
<style lang="scss" is:global>
  :root {
    --accent: 136, 58, 234;
    --accent-light: 224, 204, 250;
    --accent-dark: 49, 10, 101;
    --accent-gradient: linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      rgb(var(--accent)),
      rgb(var(--accent-light)) 30%,
      white 60%
    );
  }
  html {
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: #13151a;
  }
  code {
    font-family:
      Menlo,
      Monaco,
      Lucida Console,
      Liberation Mono,
      DejaVu Sans Mono,
      Bitstream Vera Sans Mono,
      Courier New,
      monospace;
  }
  body {
    color: #3e3a39;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    background-image: url(/background-pattern.png);
    /* background-position: center; */
    background-size: auto;
    background-repeat: repeat;
    position: relative;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  h1 {
    color: #4682ab;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h2 {
    color: #4682ab;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  h3 {
    color: #4682ab;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .content-box {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    height: 100%;
    box-shadow: rgba(99, 99, 99, 0.2) 0px 2px 8px 0px;
  }
  .header {
    background-color: rgb(70, 130, 171);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .header__logo {
    img {
      max-height: 120px;
    }
  }
  .header__content-wrap {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }
  .header__menu {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    /* flex-wrap: wrap; */
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-left: 0;
    li {
      align-self: center;
    }
  }
  .header__menu-link {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .header__menu-link:hover {
    color: #e6e6e6;
  }
  .main {
    min-height: 80vh;
  }
  .footer {
    color: #ffffff;
    background-color: rgb(70, 130, 171);
    background-image: url(/footer-background.png);
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }
  .footer__logo {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer__logo-image {
    max-width: 250px;
    max-height: 250px;
  }
  /* 針對小螢幕要可以 100% */
  .footer__description {
    max-width: 50%;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid #ffffff;
    /* text-align: center; */
  }
  @media (max-width: 991.9px) {
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 767.9px) {
    .footer__description {
      max-width: 80%;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 575.9px) {
    .footer__description {
      max-width: 95%;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 1920px) {
    .footer {
      background-position: center left;
    }
  }
</style>
